messages.message:
Do we have an internal or customer-facing overview about all 3rd Party components (open source, or closed source) we utilize internally?
I do have the list of docker images for this already but we are getting questions in particular on open sources frameworks, components as well.

Our package.json file has a list of all the external packages we use on the frontend (the ones under `dependencies` are what you'd want to look at): https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/package.json

We've bumped versions of these before after customer security audits have found that a certain version has a security vulnerability.
